## Development

Get the source:
```
git clone https://github.com/lukasbuenger/immutable-cursors
```

Install dependencies:
```
npm install
```

Lint the code:
```
npm run lint
```

Run the tests:
```
npm test
```

Build ES5/ES3:
```
npm run build
```

Build the docs / README:
```
npm run docs
```

Update all local dependencies:
```
npm run update-dependencies
```

